TopicTitle: Building an Eve Space Station with the KSO Shuttle Mod STS 123 - STS 130

Articles.Content:
The Twenty-Third of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions and Nineteenth Flight of the Tenacious! STS 123's objective is to deploy the KSO Eve Space Station Core Module and return to the KSC Runway!

The construction and deployment missions will be STS 123 through STS 130.


Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing.

STS 124 will deploy the Eve Station Science Bay.

The Twenty-Fourth of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions and Twentieth Flight of the Tenacious! STS 124's objective is to deploy the KSO Eve Space Station Science Bay and return to the KSC Runway!

The construction and deployment missions run STS 123 through STS 130.


Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing.

STS 125 will deploy the Eve Station Habitat Module #1! Edited March 10, 2014 by Westi29

STS 128 will deploy the Eve Station Propulsion Module!

The Twenty-Eighth of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions and 24th Flight of the Tenacious! STS 128's objective is to deploy the KSO Eve Space Station Propulsion Module and return to the KSC Runway! The propulsion module is a Lack Luster Labs 80kN 800Isp Nuclear engine.

The construction and deployment missions run STS 123 through STS 130.

STS 130 will deploy the Eve Station Starboard Solar Truss followed by the journey to Eve!

The Thirtieth of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions and 26th Flight of the Tenacious! STS 130's objectives are to deploy the KSO Eve Space Station Starboard Solar Truss, return to the KSC Runway, and perform the transfer to Eve!

Most of the footage is shown in 8x speed for quick viewing.
